trans-unit.source: Represents a selection of content that an annotation is anchored to.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et utvalg av innhold som en merknad er forankret til.

trans-unit.source: TextAnchor is the object type of the returned <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.IAnchorInfo.ResolvedAnchor%2A> if you are using sticky notes and highlights in flow or fixed documents.
trans-unit.target: TextAnchor er objekttypen for det returnerte <xref:System.Windows.Annotations.IAnchorInfo.ResolvedAnchor%2A>Hvis du bruker trege merknader og utheving i flyt eller fast dokumenter.</xref:System.Windows.Annotations.IAnchorInfo.ResolvedAnchor%2A>

trans-unit.source: TextAnchor is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewk](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewk-md.md)] version 3.5.
For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [versjoner og avhengigheter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
